perior way to search\nfor dark matter even if the elastic and inelastic scattering cross sections are\ncomparable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Apr 2019 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2019 12:46:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-23"}
